#

Simple Tomato Bruschetta

15 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

gluten

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free option

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

appetizereasyfresh

Description

A refreshing and crunchy appetizer with a burst of fresh tomato flavor.

Ingredients

  • french baguette: 1
  • ripe tomatoes: 2
  • garlic clove: 1
  • fresh basil leaves: a handful
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
